#* Akizuki-class Destroyers can now equip Large Radars, Large Sonars, Command Facilities and Armor Bulges.
#* Akizuki-class Destroyers now get an equipment bonus from: all [[10cm Twin High-angle Mount]] variants, [[Type 94 Anti-Aircraft Fire Director]](additional synergy with AA radars), [[Type 21 Air RADAR]], and [[Type 21 Air Radar Kai Ni]].
#* Light Cruiser gun fit bonuses have been updated for: 
